123:Pivot Interiors operates as a multi\-entity office furniture dealership with locations across multiple markets, requiring unified business intelligence and reporting capabilities to support data\-driven decision\-making across all operational areas\. The organization currently faces significant challenges with D365's reporting limitations, including problematic AP reports, unusable WIP reports requiring manual updates, and weekly AR aging reports that must be manually refreshed\. These limitations force reliance on Excel\-based workarounds and prevent realtime operational visibility\.
