_Unification/01 - CRM (Sample).md:247:- **GP discipline:** Pivot's framework as structural baseline (target + MillerKnoll mix + erosion across stages)
_Unification/01 - CRM (Sample).md:248:- **Cross-division referrals:** Pivot's workflow with real-time alerts
